229
00:29:56,760 --> 00:30:01,140
- I lost him, Goose.
- Show me what you've got, kid.

230
00:30:02,680 --> 00:30:05,850
- I lost him.
- I'm looking.

231
00:30:07,520 --> 00:30:11,690
- He's on our tail, coming hard.
- I got him. Here we go.

232
00:30:25,000 --> 00:30:29,590
- Talk to me, Goose.
