233
00:30:29,840 --> 00:30:34,300
You can run, kid, but you can't hide.

234
00:30:36,340 --> 00:30:41,220
All right, Jester,
I'll give you a run for your money here.

235
00:30:45,480 --> 00:30:47,900
Watch the mountains!

236
00:30:57,570 --> 00:31:02,830
He's still back there. Come on, Mav,
do some of that pilot shit.

237
00:31:13,300 --> 00:31:17,680
- Come on, bring it right.
- I've had about enough of this shit.

238
00:31:19,930 --> 00:31:22,970
- I'll hit the brakes, he'll fly right by.
- You're mine.

239
00:31:30,730 --> 00:31:32,690
Jesus Christ!

240
00:31:36,440 --> 00:31:40,110
- Let's see what you've got now, Jester.
- Let's turn and burn.

241
00:31:58,550 --> 00:32:02,930
- He's going vertical. So am l.
