245
00:32:39,260 --> 00:32:43,800
- Jester's dead.
- Jester's dead.

246
00:32:46,100 --> 00:32:49,770
Get your butts above the hard-deck
and return to base.

247
00:32:52,650 --> 00:32:55,810
Yes, sir!

248
00:33:00,570 --> 00:33:06,870
- This is Ghost Rider requesting a fly-by.
- Negative. The pattern is full.

249
00:33:07,120 --> 00:33:12,500
- No, Mav. This is not a good idea.
- Sorry, but it's time to buzz the tower.

250
00:33:24,010 --> 00:33:26,800
Goddamn son of a bitch!

251
00:33:30,680 --> 00:33:32,850
Great balls of fire.

252
00:33:36,730 --> 00:33:39,650
- Jester's dead.
- You won? Bullshit.

253
00:33:39,900 --> 00:33:45,530
- Didn't everybody?.
- We got our butts kicked.

254
00:33:45,780 --> 00:33:50,700
I said to Hollywood, "Where did he go?"
He said, "Where did who go?"

255
00:33:50,950 --> 00:33:56,040
- And he's laughing at us on the radio.
- That was me, dickhead. We won.

256
00:33:56,290 --> 00:34:00,800
- All right!
- They won too, man.

257
00:34:01,050 --> 00:34:04,720
- That's not what I heard.
- We got Jester.

258
00:34:04,970 --> 00:34:09,100
- Below the hard-deck doesn't count.
- We nailed that son of a bitch.

259
00:34:09,350 --> 00:34:14,440
- You guys really are cowboys.
- What's your problem, Kazansky?.

260
00:34:14,690 --> 00:34:18,900
You're everyone's problem.
