261
00:34:19,150 --> 00:34:24,950
- I don't like you. You're dangerous.
- That's right, lceman.

262
00:34:25,200 --> 00:34:28,870
I am dangerous.

263
00:34:30,370 --> 00:34:35,040
Maverick?. You and Goose
get your butts up to Viper's office, now!

