for your safety and for that of your team.

278
00:36:10,760 --> 00:36:17,310
They're not flexible, nor am l. Obey them
or you're history. Is that clear?.

279
00:36:19,520 --> 00:36:22,690
Yes, sir!

280
00:36:29,780 --> 00:36:32,360
