283
00:36:52,800 --> 00:36:57,720
Fitness report says it all.
He's a wild card.

284
00:36:57,970 --> 00:37:01,770
Completely unpredictable.

285
00:37:02,020 --> 00:37:06,150
- He got you, didn't he?
- Yeah.

286
00:37:06,400 --> 00:37:11,240
Maverick. I flew with his old man.

287
00:37:15,280 --> 00:37:21,870
Tell me, if you had to go into battle,
would you want him with you?

288
00:37:22,120 --> 00:37:25,880
I just don't know.

289
00:37:36,010 --> 00:37:39,140
- Still awake?
- Yeah.

290
00:37:42,230 --> 00:37:45,230
- What's up?
- I can't sleep.

291
00:37:47,650 --> 00:37:53,990
When I realised we were off to Top Gun,
all I could think about was that trophy.

292
00:37:54,240 --> 00:37:59,450
I've got to be straight with you, Mav.
Right now, I just hope we graduate.

293
00:38:02,120 --> 00:38:07,040
