It's a little bit too aggressive.

303
00:39:26,000 --> 00:39:30,420
Too aggressive?

304
00:39:30,670 --> 00:39:35,760
I guess when I see something,
I go right after it.

305
00:39:36,010 --> 00:39:41,890
- You didn't tell me who you were.
- I didn't get a chance. You deserved it.

306
00:39:43,560 --> 00:39:51,610
