398
00:55:33,260 --> 00:55:38,510
I fell the need ...
the need for speed.

399
00:55:41,760 --> 00:55:47,520
This is hop 19. Multiple aircraft, multiple
bogeys. Your training is halfover.

400
00:55:47,770 --> 00:55:52,320
The competltion for the trophy
remains tight. Firstplace, lceman.

401
00:55:52,570 --> 00:55:55,820
Second, Maverick, two points behind.

402
00:55:56,070 --> 00:55:59,570
