407
00:56:36,990 --> 00:56:40,950
Hollywood, you lead. I'll cover you.

408
00:56:51,710 --> 00:56:54,000
Break now, Jester.

409
00:56:58,050 --> 00:57:01,180
We're losing Viper.
Let's just stay on Jester.

410
00:57:05,680 --> 00:57:12,940
- Goose, find Viper. He's out there.
- Stay with Hollywood.

411
00:57:13,190 --> 00:57:17,900
- There's Viper. Three o'clock low.
- We're Hollywood's cover.

412
00:57:18,150 --> 00:57:22,200
- Don't you leave me.
- Hollywood, you're looking good.

413
00:57:22,450 --> 00:57:24,530
I'm going after Viper.

414
00:57:27,160 --> 00:57:30,120
- Goddamn you!
