417
00:57:45,800 --> 00:57:49,230
Holy shit. We're head-to-head.

418
00:58:03,360 --> 00:58:06,740
Rock and roll! Here's our big chance.

419
00:58:09,450 --> 00:58:12,540
Come on, goddamn it.

420
00:58:14,750 --> 00:58:17,550
Come on, keep coming.

421
00:58:20,670 --> 00:58:24,640
Okay, sidewinder missile selected.
Come on, baby.

422
00:58:24,250 --> 00:58:26,750
Come around. That's it.

423
00:58:32,750 --> 00:58:40,390
- Jesus, he's good. Where's he going?
