424
00:58:43,310 --> 00:58:46,810
Come on, baby.

425
00:58:50,060 --> 00:58:52,860
Damn, this kid's good.

426
00:58:53,110 --> 00:58:56,690
He's too close for missiles.
I'm switching to guns.

427
00:58:58,950 --> 00:59:02,280
Come on, come on.

428
00:59:03,240 --> 00:59:06,040
Stick with it ...

429
00:59:09,000 --> 00:59:13,040
- Hold it. Check our tail.
- Shit, there's Jester!

430
00:59:13,290 --> 00:59:18,170
