434
00:59:41,740 --> 00:59:46,490
That was some of the best flying
I've seen yet. Until you got killed.

435
00:59:46,740 --> 00:59:51,420
You never, never leave your wingman.

436
00:59:56,460 --> 01:00:02,270
Maverick ... It's not your flying,
it's your attitude.

437
01:00:03,650 --> 01:00:10,990
The enemy's dangerous, but right now
you're worse. Dangerous and foolish.

438
01:00:11,240 --> 01:00:18,280
You may not like who's flying with you,
but whose side are you on?

439
01:00:25,990 --> 01:00:32,550
At least Viper got lceman before
he got us. We've still got a shot at it.

440
01:00:32,800 --> 01:00:38,890
That was stupid, I know better than that.
That will never happen again.

441
01:00:41,730 --> 01:00:45,020
I know ...

