618
01:30:46,440 --> 01:30:51,950
Ice, we've got a problem. I have four
aircraft on radar. Four bogeys.

619
01:30:52,200 --> 01:30:54,990
Wood, we've got four bogeys.

620
01:30:56,700 --> 01:31:00,790
- Wrong, make that five!
- There's five, sir.

621
01:31:03,000 --> 01:31:06,170
- Oh, shit!
- He's got a radar lock on us.

622
01:31:08,670 --> 01:31:11,170
Get out of there, Hollywood!

623
01:31:20,280 --> 01:31:25,610
I'm hit. We're coming apart.
I can't control it! We're going down.

624
01:31:25,860 --> 01:31:28,790
Wood's been hit. Wood's been hit!

625
01:31:29,030 --> 01:31:32,290
Voodoo One, Wood's been hit.
We've lost Hollywood!

626
01:31:32,540 --> 01:31:35,710
- We've lostHollywood.
- Launch Maverick.

627
01:31:35,960 --> 01:31:41,000
Get a bearing on Hollywood and
Wolfman. Launch the rescue helicopter.

628
01:32:06,820 --> 01:32:11,330
- Iceman, what's your position?
- 090 at 180 miles.

629
01:32:11,580 --> 01:32:16,170
- They're coming in left.
- Three MiGs dead ahead.

630
01:32:18,330 --> 01:32:23,050
I'm going after them.
I'm bringing it around to the left.

631
01:32:23,300 --> 01:32:27,720
We have four on our tail.
That makes six of them!

632
01:32:32,970 --> 01:32:38,150
- He's firing. Break right.
- This is Voodoo One. We are defensive.

633
01:32:38,400 --> 01:32:42,940
- Launch the alertfiighters!
- 160 miles and closing in fast, sir.

634
01:32:43,190 --> 01:32:44,860
Ready Willard and Simkin.

635
01:32:47,990 --> 01:32:53,620
- I'll be there in 30 seconds.
- I'm engaged with five. I'm in deep shit.

636
01:32:56,410 --> 01:33:01,380
- Willard and Simkin?
- We can't launch any aircraft yet, sir.

637
01:33:01,630 --> 01:33:06,090
How long? 10 minutes?
It's over in two minutes!

638
01:33:08,800 --> 01:33:12,730
One MiG 12 o'clock high ...
Watch your back!

639
01:33:18,730 --> 01:33:23,330
- Break right!
- Shit, that was close.

640
01:33:23,580 --> 01:33:27,120
- Maverick, getyourbutt down here!
